snippet.title: Lost Soul Aside - Pre-Order Trailer | PS5 & PC Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/lost-soul-aside/ 

Fight to save your world. Save your sister. Save your soul.

Embark on an epic odyssey to save your sister and the whole of humankind from dimensional invaders.

Pre-order Lost Soul Aside from February 19th.
